<paragraph id="97724EADB24002B3C24ECF0A3EE688B4" pageNumber="774">Etymology</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C2CE06995C43E5ED27C746D7F84F80C3" pageNumber="774">This species is dedicated to a prominent specialist on Chrysomelid beetles, professor Andrzej Warchalqwski, celebrating his 80th birthday.</paragraph>
